data.description: Canarsie: Big Beautiful Brick... Priced to Sell! Legal 2 Family with 2 Car Private Drive & Built-in Garage in Front and Private Backyard! Both Apartments have 3 Bedrooms, Large Living Room & Updated eat-in Kitchens! Owner's Apartment has a Terrace & Master Bedroom with Bath & Jacuzzi as well! Plus on the Walk-in Level you have an Additional Family Room, Kitchenette, Bedrooom, Bath & Laundry! Many Updates including Heat, Hot Water & Roof! Well Maintained & Excellent Condition throughout! $1500/Month Rental Income! Very economical! Great Location! Will be delivered Vacant! Why rent when you can own for less! Asking $549K!
